<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1916-07-13T23:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1916-07-13T23:00:00-05:00" n="1028" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1028">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.48/3320</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Consul <persName type="from">Garrett</persName> to the
                                    <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Laredo, Texas</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-07-13T22:00:00-06:00">
                                    <hi rend="italic">July 13, 1916, 10 p.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Chamal colonists in mountain sent a messenger to me requesting me to ask
                            Department’s assistance to get them out as they have been robbed until
                            they have neither food nor money to reach border and <pb facs="0780" n="704" xml:id="pg_704"/> this is why they have not come. The
                            cheapest and best route is through Laredo, and if Department will
                            authorize me to do so I will send one of the colony from here and bring
                            them out.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Garrett</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>